Maintainer: Markus Voge <markus.voge@ea-aw.de>
Description: Data objects in R that describe a morphological field can be
    rendered as HTML tables using the JavaScript library 'DataTables' (via
    Shiny). The 'DataTables' library has been included in this R package.
    The package is built upon RStudio's excellent R package 'DT'.
URL: https://github.com/sgrubsmyon/morphr
